highlights.text: Annika has the most spots on Top Songs Denmark. “Stolt (feat. Lamin)” is the highest at #7.
“Reposado” by Benny Jamz and Gilli has been on Top Songs Denmark the longest, at 450 days straight.
“Confident” by Justin Bieber and Chance the Rapper is the highest new entry on Top Songs Denmark at #187.
“Dronning Af Månen” by Pil is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Denmark, up 58 spots at #131.
